Text.Value: What happens to the bodies of those that 'ascend'?
Left flesh... joined with Her... eternally...
*The corpse remains silent. That was more of a comment than a question, really.*
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis: The Speak With Dead dialog for the corpse hidden behind the mind flayer membranes in the bloodbath section of the Oubliette. This corpse is currently a goblin, but its race and backstory can be changed at the writer's behest.
